imdb.plot outline: In this video series you'll discover how to de-clutter in all areas of your life so you can finally "breathe". How to accept and learn from your mistakes and to train your mind to replace negative thoughts with positive ones. We'll go over how to set and achieve your short and long term goals for happiness and much more.
